#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:1
msgid "E3022"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:3
msgid "Ill-formed list of alerts."
msgstr "alert 列表格式不正确。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:5
msgid ""
"This error happens when the `alert-list` field in `moon.pkg` cannot be "
"parsed. The field uses the same compact list syntax as `warn-list`, with "
"`+` to enable an alert, `-` to disable an alert, and `@` to enable it as "
"an error."
msgstr ""
"当 `moon.pkg` 中的 `alert-list` 字段无法解析时，会发生此错误。该字段使用与 `warn-list` "
"相同的紧凑列表语法：用 `+` 启用 alert，用 `-` 禁用 alert，用 `@` 将其作为错误启用。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:9
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:11
msgid ""
"options(\n"
"  \"alert-list\": \"1\",\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:17
msgid "Use a valid alert-list entry:"
msgstr "使用有效的 alert-list 条目："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E3022.md:19
msgid ""
"options(\n"
"  \"alert-list\": \"-unsafe\",\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""
